videos.headline: Amari Bailey gets fancy for UCLA's opening bucket
videos.description: Amari Bailey dribbles behind his back and scores a layup for UCLA's opening points.

videos.headline: Arizona wins Pac-12 tourney after UCLA misses an open look
videos.description: Azuolas Tubelis misses a free throw and UCLA has a chance to win it but Dylan Andrews' 3-pointer is off the mark to seal the Pac-12 tournament title for Arizona.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Arizona wins Pac-12 tourney after UCLA misses an open look) 2023/03/11
